textAfterTable: Profile ICON Utilities Fund operates as a open ended investment fund The Fund provides long term capital investment opportunities to individuals and businesses. The Fund invests at least 80% of its net assets, plus any borrowings for investment purposes, in equity securities of companies in the Utilities sector. ICON Utilities Fund offers research and technological tools.
